      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable choice for everyday transportation. While the engine and transmission are in good working order, the car shows clear signs of its age, including some minor exterior scratches and noticeable wear on the interior upholstery. It is a solid, functional vehicle for someone who prioritizes reliability over aesthetics.",
